nodes.caption: What a day! Colindale mini-festival. A disaster, really, struck as the pipes burst and the floor collapsed in our venue 16 hours before KO was due. Disaster turned to triumph as everyone pitched in and we improvised an outdoor festival, on the green in the heart of #grahamepark estate. Thank you all! A brilliant group of local people and organisations, scientists, engineers, artists, volunteers and the wonderful people who visited and participated. Such a warm, enthusiastic and joyous experience. In the community, with the community! #STEM #STEAM #smashfestuk #middlesexuniversity #RAE #ukspaceagency #publicengagement #participation #survivalvillage #spacecamp And a huge thank you to #splento @splentoapp for the fab photos!
